txt.en:
The Orcs of Nan Wathren only grow stronger and more cruel as you press farther into the pass.

You should defeat the Tarkrîp Shankers and Brawlers you encounter as you make your way through the eastern edge of Nan Wathren.

<rgb=#FF0000>Fellowship recommended.</rgb>
You have defeated a number of Orcs from Nan Wathren.
The Orcs of Nan Wathren only grow stronger and more cruel as you press farther into the pass.

You have defeated a number of the strongest Orcs in eastern Nan Wathren. These foes were hardy and numerous, and your valiant endeavour to beat them back has earned you great renown amongst the Free Peoples of Middle-earth.
Defeat Tarkrîp Brawlers in western Nan Wathren ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Defeat Tarkrîp Shankers in western Nan Wathren ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

Tarkrîp Shankers and Brawlers can be found in eastern Nan Wathren, in the southern North Downs.

You should defeat a number of Tarkrîp Shankers and Brawlers in Nan Wathren.

<rgb=#FF0000>Fellowship recommended.</rgb>
